 Duane Syndrome Global Portal - Implementation Plan                                                                                                                                   
                                                 
 Context                             

 Building a comprehensive global portal for Duane Syndrome at duane-syndrome.com / duane.life. The site will serve patients, parents, and friends worldwide with medical information,
  community resources, interactive tools, a specialist directory, and community-contributed content. It must be multilingual (English + Hebrew minimum), mobile-first, SEO-optimized,
  and low-maintenance. Budget: ~$0-20/month.

