 Feature List (Ordered by Implementation Priority)

 Each feature is standalone and deployable. Features build on each other logically.

 Phase 1: Foundation

 F01 - Project Scaffolding & Dev Setup
 - Initialize Next.js 16 with App Router (React 19), TypeScript, Tailwind CSS v4, ESLint, Turbopack
 - Configure next-intl with English + Hebrew, RTL support
 - Set up middleware for locale detection/routing
 - Create base layout with responsive shell (header, footer, nav placeholder)
 - Configure Vercel deployment from GitHub
 - Add robots.txt, basic sitemap, favicon/metadata
 - Deploys: Empty but functional bilingual site at the domain

 F02 - Design System & UI Components
 - Define color palette (soft, empowering: teal/coral/warm neutrals with good contrast)
 - Typography: accessible font pairing that supports Latin + Hebrew glyphs
 - Build shared UI kit: Button, Card, Input, Modal, Badge, Skeleton, Toast
 - Responsive navigation with mobile hamburger menu
 - Locale switcher component
 - Dark/light mode (optional, light default)
 - Deploys: Polished, empty shell with consistent design language

 F03 - Home Page & Persona Selector
 - Hero section: empowering message, what Duane Syndrome is in one sentence
 - Persona selector: "I have Duane Syndrome" / "I'm a parent" / "I'm a friend/family"
 - Store persona choice in cookie/localStorage, adjust content throughout site
 - Featured content cards (blog posts, latest research, community spotlight)
 - Quick links to key sections
 - Newsletter signup inline CTA
 - Deploys: Welcoming entry point that routes users to relevant content

 Phase 2: Content Foundation

 F04 - Sanity CMS Integration & Blog System
 - Set up Sanity project, define blogPost + author schemas
 - Embed Sanity Studio at /admin with auth
 - Blog listing page with pagination, tag filtering, locale filtering
 - Individual blog post page with portable text rendering
 - ISR: revalidate on Sanity webhook
 - Reading time estimate
 - SEO: Open Graph images via @vercel/og, structured data (Article schema)
 - Deploys: Admin can create/publish blog posts, SEO-optimized

 F05 - Medical Information Pages (About Duane)
 - Sanity schema: medicalPage with sections, sources, last-reviewed date
 - Pages: Overview, Types (1/2/3), Symptoms, Diagnosis, Treatments (conventional + alternative)
 - Treatments subsections: prism glasses, eye patches, surgery options, vision therapy, botox
