 Hosting & Deployment Setup

 1. Vercel: Connect GitHub repo → auto-deploy on push to main, preview deploys on PRs
 2. Domain: Point duane-syndrome.com and duane.life to Vercel (CNAME/A records). Use duane-syndrome.com as primary (better for SEO - descriptive domain), duane.life redirects to it
 3. Sanity: Create project at sanity.io, free plan. Studio embedded in app.
 4. Turso: Create database at turso.tech, free plan. Get connection URL + auth token for Vercel env vars.
 5. Auth.js: Register OAuth apps at Google Cloud Console + Facebook Developer Portal. Add client IDs/secrets to Vercel env vars.
 6. Resend: Create account, verify domain for sending. Add API key to Vercel env vars.
 7. GitHub Actions: Add secrets for PubMed API key (free from NCBI), Gemini API key (free tier from Google AI Studio), Turso credentials.

