 SEO Strategy

 - Primary domain: duane-syndrome.com (descriptive, keyword-rich)
 - Schema.org markup on every page: MedicalCondition, MedicalWebPage, FAQPage, Article, Physician, BreadcrumbList
 - Sitemap: auto-generated per locale via next-sitemap
 - Hreflang tags: on every page linking English ↔ Hebrew (and future languages)
 - OG images: auto-generated branded images via @vercel/og
 - Pillar content strategy: comprehensive 2-5K word pages targeting "Duane syndrome [topic]" keywords
 - Freshness signals: auto-updated research feed, regular blog posts
 - Google Search Console: submit sitemaps for both domains, monitor indexing
 - Structured data testing: validate with Google Rich Results Test before each feature launch

 ---
 Verification & Testing Strategy

 - Per feature: Manual QA on desktop + mobile (iOS Safari, Android Chrome), both English and Hebrew
 - Automated: Playwright E2E tests for critical flows (subscribe, submit content, search)
 - Lighthouse CI: Run in GitHub Actions, fail build if performance/accessibility drops below thresholds
 - Content preview: Sanity preview mode for draft content before publishing
 - Staging: Vercel preview deploys serve as staging for every PR